Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:24.94,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:29.43,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.54,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.79,0:00:35.76,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.11,0:00:39.82,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:44.76,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:50.27,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:56.30,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:58.99,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:03.51,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.08,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:09.88,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:14.87,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.72,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:26.98,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:30.07,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:35.86,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
