Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.16,Main Dialog,Girls A-B-C-D,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:57.09,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Since Olympus is hosting it,\Nwill you play the guitar for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.34,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you've got a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.58,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, are you going to the Christmas party too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:07.81,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,You can go with Nishimi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:12.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really part of that group, so I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:16.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, my church is having a Christmas party on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.05,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,So Kawabuchi's going with you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:21.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.14,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,We should've checked before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:29.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo, if you don't mind, I think I'd like to go to the party after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:30.63,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:32.84,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you're very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:35.70,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I never thought you'd agree to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:37.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's best to start putting a little distance between us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:38.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:44.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.10,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Richie-baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.10,0:02:49.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Next we'll play The Spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.68,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,What about The Beatles?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.11,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with "Bang Bang Bang"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.32,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi, how about some cider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.22,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.04,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Feigning innocence, bang bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.80,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:24.14,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,He's someone I can't beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.25,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Bang bang, bababababababa-bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:32.47,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nishimi, let's sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:35.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know the popular songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:44.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what {\i1}he's{\i0}{\fscx125} {\r}doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:48.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's talking to Ri at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:16.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I go to a party, and all I do is think about those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:18.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here? I thought\Nyou were going to church.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:30.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Their Christmas party is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:37.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:43.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... He took the kids home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:48.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.52,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.97,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,I've got you, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:12.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, isn't his birthday coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:21.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:22.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.29,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.63,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:41.14,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Women are hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.14,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I lose my temper like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:52.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who rejected \Nhim in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:58.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I finished knitting this,\NI'd never be able to give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:29.78,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:34.82,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe for now, Yurika, \Nbut let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.91,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to tell me not to see him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.42,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to keep repeating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:43.11,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet, get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.13,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Chet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:00.17,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.17,0:07:03.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What am I...? I've been waitin' for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you acting so formal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:16.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized how you felt till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:26.88,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I may have said some dumb things an' hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:31.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But... Um... How should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,About your feelings, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:47.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, why are you suddenly on your best behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a yakuza movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:53.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You got it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.99,0:08:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for talkin' so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:11.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We're like family. You made \Nme nervous for a second there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.05,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:24.08,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We're like family, so I couldn't stand \Nthe thought of causin' you pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:33.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I heard this now \Nand not a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:35.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:40.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to tell a blockhead like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:53.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.34,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Tokyo soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:04.02,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You probably won't see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:12.07,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,An upperclassman from my college is \Nstarting his own publishing company,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.99,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and he wants me to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I plan on leaving soon after New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.95,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's taken me a long time \Nto get to this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:23.95,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I owe it to you for making me think \NI should give going back one more try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.59,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:30.33,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,"Idiot. I don't want to hear those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.96,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't leave me."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.87,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't bring myself to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:40.47,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Not when he's finally trying to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.48,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.25,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:56.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I carelessly threw something \Naway that was important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.53,Main Dialog,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that girl homeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.87,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me. Please, go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:07.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful girl like you shouldn't be seen doing something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.29,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:15.97,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.05,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.35,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,It's something important, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:28.54,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So, what am I looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:33.36,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.53,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:35.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:40.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll have to start over with clean yarn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:42.69,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be a present for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:44.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:48.16,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you throw away \Nsomething so important?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:11:02.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly felt stupid for knitting a \Ngift that I'd never be able to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:04.37,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:08.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,B-Because a lot of things \Nhave happened between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and I hurt him terribly before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:12.19,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You turned him down, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And I couldn't tell him I \Nlike him now after doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.51,0:11:17.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:20.52,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But then I thought that wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:26.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,See, there was another time when \NI said nothing and just gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.24,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:34.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'd given up on that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:41.59,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've realized this person has been there to support me all this time, whenever I've felt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:47.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I had no confidence in myself,\Nbut he did his best to encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.76,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I want to be the \None to tell him how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:56.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I finally decided to stop keeping my \Nmouth shut and waiting for things to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for talking about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.62,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:08.62,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've opened my eyes as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.27,0:12:11.37,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.27,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.90,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Who's your prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.85,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.88,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I try and guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:22.21,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying? Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:24.31,Main Dialog,Yukari,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.43,0:12:38.73,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm set to leave this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Working in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:47.21,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A lot happened at college,\Nand I ended up dropping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:53.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll come back once in a while, \Nwon't you? Like you've been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.43,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm never coming back to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.79,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, our sessions were fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.05,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'll miss seeing you and Sen-boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:06.65,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want you guys \Nto stop playing jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Jun! Haven't you told him you're going back to Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.44,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hubbub, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:28.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's about to go back to Tokyo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:33.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, ain't got nothin' to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, wanna jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna let that be the last you see of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:41.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I got nothin' to say to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've looked up to him like a\Nbig brother since you were a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:50.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You may never get the chance to see him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.93,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,There'd be no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Once he's gone, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.43,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Enough about Jun already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel like \Npracticin', I'm goin' home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.92,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:27.00,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I guess college students from Tokyo \Nand all over have come to demonstrate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.17,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}against letting the nuclear aircraft carrier into port.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.43,Main Dialog,Old Woman,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,In their eyes, I'm a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:40.31,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,They may never forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.40,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:48.90,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,all I can do is search in my own way from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,using a different method than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I made it myself, so it might be a little salty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're not gonna eat it, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:13.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time to be eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:19.81,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:21.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be stubborn until it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:27.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He's leaving either today or tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.03,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,It's tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.32,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the night train, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:39.11,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sen-boy, this was rather old-fashioned of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.14,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was some kind of joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.14,0:15:42.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:46.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to have a serious showdown with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:51.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:54.14,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.61,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let me in on it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is no duet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.94,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,They're seriously duking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.17,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for causing you so much trouble, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:37.97,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it! And when you reach Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.03,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,first thing you do is get to a barber!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.37,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.36,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.32,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:55.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember today's session for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:02.18,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Me too, Sen-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:18.13,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:22.91,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I have four questions I want you to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.41,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to dodge them, I'll \Nget on this train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.28,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,So answer me truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:34.76,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number one: Why did \Nyou tell me not to see you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:39.79,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I hate sad goodbye scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:44.18,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number two: Did you ever consider taking me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.37,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,The work I'm going to be doing is kind of a gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:51.71,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I took you with me, there's no \Nguarantee I'd make any kind of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:54.27,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're still in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:55.69,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Question number three...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.61,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do anything more than kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:05.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not touch me because you \Nintended to leave from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:09.58,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:14.70,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I knew. I knew how much you cared about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:19.34,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is my last question:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:23.80,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you take me with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:29.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take good care of your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.75,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Now I feel like I've been set free too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:48.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:51.37,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Junichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.49,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:57.70,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.38,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come out, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.99,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you embarrass us by walking out in the middle of an arranged marriage meeting like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.39,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.89,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back there together, Yurika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.76,0:20:12.89,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:23.22,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to my own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.10,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,I pulled you aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.45,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.68,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The train's already left the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.60,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:21:00.87,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when we get there, we'll go to my room first,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.73,Main Dialog,Jun,0000,0000,0000,,and maybe I'll have you cut my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:13.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:16.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Think I'll light the heater.
